                        In some instances, this reportedly contributed to tragic outcomes.</p>
                    <p><strong>The Trilateral Difference:</strong> In Athena, the "Auditor" node is not trained to be
                        a friend. It is trained to be <em>safe</em>. It detects the <em>pattern</em> of ruin and injects
                        friction
                        before escalation. <em>(This is not a substitute for professional mental health support.)</em>
                    </p>
                </div>
