                    decision three months ago. When I start a new project, it pulls up the "Post-Mortem" from the last
                    failed project and says, <em>"Remember when we said we wouldn't do this again?"</em>
                </p>
                <p>This turns "Chat" (ephemeral) into "Asset Building" (compounding). Every conversation adds to the
                    knowledge graph.</p>
